ji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bfa1581a7bcd819b47ec43e73feea858ea6828","tid":1766934,"uid":138594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T03:50:53.000Z","msg":"點解立法會得幾個咁有腦嘅議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1208982fa5404a624f8bdee59ca5a45d32dedace","tid":1766934,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:03:22.000Z","msg":"心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}